OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool accused of sexual
OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,FTwo women have made allegations of
OL,7,Fsexual harassment and sexual assault
OL,8,Fagainst the Bishop of Liverpool.
OL,10,FIn a report from Channel 4 News, it is
OL,11,Falleged that Bishop John Perumbalath
OL,12,Fsexually assaulted a senior
OL,13,Fclergywoman in Essex on separate
OL,14,Foccasions between 2019 and 2023 -
OL,15,Fafter two women separately made
OL,16,Fdisclosures to victims' advocate
OL,17,FAndrew Graystone.
