OL,6,FOne woman said: "He held me there and
OL,7,Fkissed me forcefully on my mouth,
OL,8,Fwhich I did not like and I did not
OL,9,Fwant.
OL,11,F"I tried to move away, but he was
OL,12,Fholding my head too tightly. I could
OL,13,Ffeel his mouth pressing on my mouth. I
OL,14,Fcould feel some of his saliva, and the
OL,15,Ftexture of his beard around my mouth."
OL,26,@nD@QOUwD@fO]
