OL,6,FThe same woman also claims he groped
OL,7,Fher: "As he was letting go of hugging
OL,8,Fme, he ran his hands past the side of
OL,9,Fmy breasts on both sides, with a
OL,10,Fmedium pressure, until he reached the
OL,11,Fedge of the areola.
OL,13,F"He pressed his face against my face,
OL,14,Fsaid 'I love you' quietly in my ear,
OL,15,Fand moved his mouth to just below my
OL,16,Fear, on the pulse point on my neck. He
OL,17,Fopened his mouth, took a piece of my
OL,18,Fskin between his lips, and let go."
OL,26,@oD@FOUuD@AOUzD@cO]
