OL,6,FResponding to the allegations, Bishop
OL,7,FJohn confirmed to Channel 4 that he
OL,8,Fwas investigated by police and
OL,9,Finterviewed under caution, but no
OL,10,Ffurther action was taken.
OL,12,FAnother Bishop, among 31 serving women
OL,13,FBishops in the Church of England, also
OL,14,Ftold Channel 4 News that she was
OL,15,Fallegedly sexually harassed by the
OL,16,FBishop of Liverpool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
