OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,FShe says she also made a formal
OL,7,Fcomplaint in 2024 - but it has emerged
OL,8,Fa judge refused to allow it because
OL,9,Fmore than a year had passed since the
OL,10,Falleged harassment.
OL,12,FDespite the allegations, Bishop John
OL,13,Fwas enthroned in the Liverpool diocese
OL,14,Fin April 2023.
OL,16,FChannel 4 has also reported that the
OL,17,Finterim head of the Church Archbishop
OL,18,FStephen was made aware of the
OL,19,Fallegations after Bishop John was
OL,20,Fpromoted, but before he was enthroned
OL,21,Fas Bishop of Liverpool in April 2023.
