OL,6,FArchbishop Stephen and Bishop John
OL,7,Fboth served together in the Chelmsford
OL,8,Fdiocese.
OL,10,FThe allegations were made to Andrew
OL,11,FGraystone, a victims advocate and
OL,12,Fauthor.
OL,14,FSpeaking to Channel 4, he said: "It's
OL,15,Freally shocking. You don't expect this
OL,16,Fof a senior member of a church."
