OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool accused of sexual
OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,F"It could well be another instance of
OL,7,Fa church cover up. I think one of the
OL,8,Fdifficulties at the heart of the top
OL,9,Fof our church is that there is a
OL,10,Fprotectionist culture between bishops
OL,11,Fin relation to bishops behaviour. And
OL,12,Flots of us know that happens all the
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,F"Either it seems that a complaint has
OL,16,Fbeen made to another bishop in which
OL,17,Fthat bishop has not actually actioned
OL,18,Fthe appropriate safeguarding measures,
OL,19,Fwhich would have been to step the
OL,20,Fbishop off from public administration
OL,21,Funtil the proper investigation."
