OL,6,FResponding to the allegations, Bishop
OL,7,FJohn Perumbalath said: "The
OL,8,Fallegations set out in this programme
OL,9,Fare in relation to encounters that
OL,10,Ftook place in public settings, with
OL,11,Fother people present.
OL,13,F"I have consistently denied the
OL,14,Fallegations made against me by both
OL,15,Fcomplainants. I have complied with any
OL,16,Finvestigation from the National
OL,17,FSafeguarding Team. The allegations
OL,18,Fraised in Essex were also investigated
OL,19,Fby the Police who took no further
OL,20,Faction.
OL,26,@oD@XOU
