OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool accused of sexual
OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,F"Whilst I don't believe I have done
OL,7,Fanything wrong, I have taken seriously
OL,8,Fthe lessons learnt through this
OL,9,Fprocess addressing how my actions can
OL,10,Fbe perceived by others.
OL,12,F"I will comply with any investigation
OL,13,Fdeemed necessary. I take safeguarding
OL,14,Fvery seriously and work hard to
OL,15,Fprovide proper leadership in this
OL,16,Farea".
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@EO]
