OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool accused of sexual
OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,F"The complaint was looked into
OL,7,Faccording to statutory safeguarding
OL,8,Fguidance in an NST-led process and an
OL,9,Findependent risk assessment undertaken.
OL,11,F"This process concluded that there
OL,12,Fwere no ongoing safeguarding concerns,
OL,13,Fbut a learning outcome was identified
OL,14,Fwith which the bishop fully engaged.
OL,16,F"The complaint was also investigated
OL,17,Fby the police which resulted in no
OL,18,Ffurther action.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
