OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool accused of sexual
OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,F"Some time subsequently, after hearing
OL,7,Fthe details of the complaint directly
OL,8,Ffrom the complainant, the Lead
OL,9,FSafeguarding Bishop also offered
OL,10,Fadvice and support to the woman if she
OL,11,Fwished to bring a CDM complaint. That
OL,12,Foffer also remains.
OL,14,F"While we do not discuss specific
OL,15,Fdetails of individual cases, this
OL,16,Fmatter was taken very seriously while
OL,17,Fprotecting the confidentiality of the
OL,18,Fcomplainant.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
