OL,3,CBishop of Liverpool accused of sexual
OL,4,Charassment
OL,6,F"Shortly after the start of this
OL,7,Fprocess a further disclosure was made
OL,8,Fby another woman. The information
OL,9,Fbrought by the second complainant was
OL,10,Fexplored and assessed not to be a
OL,11,Fsafeguarding matter but a matter of
OL,12,Falleged misconduct. Pastoral support
OL,13,Fhas been provided throughout for the
OL,14,Fsecond complainant and is ongoing.
OL,16,F"The second complainant did not bring
OL,17,Fa CDM complaint within the one-year
OL,18,Fdeadline. She later applied for
OL,19,Fpermission to bring it after the
OL,20,Fdeadline, which the Archbishop of York
OL,21,Ffully supported.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
