OL,6,F"However, this was refused by an
OL,7,Findependent judge, the Deputy
OL,8,FPresident of Tribunals.
OL,10,F"Archbishop Stephen has supported the
OL,11,Fcomplainant pastorally throughout the
OL,12,Fprocess and continues to offer
OL,13,Fpractical help. He had no part in the
OL,14,Fdecision making around safeguarding or
OL,15,Fdisciplinary matters."
